714060f-a.title: Manhattan: 60th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
714060f-a.text:
232-224 East 60th Street, south side, between Second and
Third Avenues, St. Thomas Chapel, (Protestant Episcopal), whch
was built in 1872, is seen 1n the foreground.
October 20, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
